367
00:25:17,480 --> 00:25:18,720
Thanks.

368
00:25:22,120 --> 00:25:23,560
Sorry. Hang on.

369
00:25:25,400 --> 00:25:26,400
Got it.

370
00:25:26,480 --> 00:25:27,760
There you go.

371
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:47,160
Who the hell is Claude Minkins?

372
00:25:50,640 --> 00:25:52,720
It's '"was,'" I'm afraid. He died.

373
00:25:52,880 --> 00:25:54,720
Tell me he had insurance.

374
00:25:55,360 --> 00:25:56,600
That's not at all likely.

375
00:25:56,680 --> 00:26:00,040
