is your business.

379
00:26:09,040 --> 00:26:10,840
Let's get it into your head.

380
00:26:10,920 --> 00:26:13,760
This is not England,
or the Royal Shakespeare...

381
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:16,240
...Taxpayer-Pick-Up-The-Tab
Health Care System.

382
00:26:16,320 --> 00:26:18,600
Somebody has to pay for this shit.

383
00:26:20,480 --> 00:26:21,720
Sorry.

384
00:26:25,360 --> 00:26:29,600
He's got liver damage, but no hepatitis.
He's HIV-negative...

385
00:26:29,760 --> 00:26:31,560
...but look at his T cell count.

386
00:26:31,640 --> 00:26:34,920
-He's negative viral and bacterial--
-What is that?

387
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:37,440
I don't know.
She probably just got her bill.

388
00:26:37,640 --> 00:26:39,120
Please help.

389
00:26:40,160 --> 00:26:42,400
Does this make sense to you? Take a look.

390
00:26:42,480 --> 00:26:45,600
