will you take the screamer?

391
00:26:46,160 --> 00:26:48,960
Very sick dude. Very funny labs.
Catch you later.

392
00:26:55,320 --> 00:26:59,080
I do. I'm sorry. I realize it is very late.
I apologize.

393
00:26:59,160 --> 00:27:01,240
Could you just answer me one thing?

394
00:27:01,360 --> 00:27:04,520
Does your hospital use
a silver-colored bracelet?

395
00:27:05,560 --> 00:27:06,600
Okay, terrific.

396
00:27:06,680 --> 00:27:11,040
You don't know any hospital or anything
that does use something like that?

397
00:27:12,520 --> 00:27:16,200
Thank you. I apologize again.
Thank you very much.

398
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:18,960
-Move, please!
-Your rays are back.

399
00:27:19,040 --> 00:27:22,480
-Thanks. In a minute.
-Someone gonna move Mrs. Gardner?

400
00:27:22,960 --> 00:27:24,840
Guy, Line 6.

401
00:27:25,320 --> 00:27:27,280
Thanks. Excuse me.

402
00:27:28,800 --> 00:27:31,360
Thanks very much for calling back.

403
00:27:31,640 --> 00:27:35,800
I'm looking for an autopsy report
on a patient called Claude Minkins.

404
00:27:36,240 --> 00:27:38,880
It would be early hours
of yesterday morning.

405
00:27:39,640 --> 00:27:41,880
Just looking for a cause of death.

406
00:27:42,040 --> 00:27:43,600
I'll hold, thanks.

407
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:49,520
And that's it?

408
00:27:50,240 --> 00:27:51,720
That's all you have?

409
00:27:51,800 --> 00:27:53,640
