00:28:09,360 --> 00:28:11,920
All right. No, forget it. Forget it.

415
00:28:12,440 --> 00:28:14,760
No, really, thank you. I have to go.

416
00:28:14,880 --> 00:28:17,760
I understand.
Thank you very much for calling back.

417
00:28:28,240 --> 00:28:29,520
Did he bite?

418
00:28:30,960 --> 00:28:32,920
One down, one to go.

419
00:28:33,840 --> 00:28:35,400
How we doing on Dolson?

420
00:28:36,320 --> 00:28:40,800
-We've been through a dozen shelters.
-Fourteen. Plus the hospitals.

421
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:44,120
We're making runs through
Grand Central twice a day.

422
00:28:45,080 --> 00:28:46,640
Okay. Keep pushing.

423
00:28:47,840 --> 00:28:50,840
I guess we're looking
for a body by now, but....

424
00:28:53,960 --> 00:28:55,560
