426
00:29:00,200 --> 00:29:02,040
I'll make out a list.

427
00:29:25,400 --> 00:29:27,200
Perhaps you're mistaken?

428
00:29:29,640 --> 00:29:31,320
I don't see how that's possible.

429
00:29:31,400 --> 00:29:33,160
With whom did you speak?

430
00:29:33,240 --> 00:29:36,600
I didn't get a name.
Someone here who called me back.

431
00:29:37,000 --> 00:29:38,640
At 1:00 in the morning.

432
00:29:39,280 --> 00:29:42,280
Gave you a cause of death,
which you didn't believe.

433
00:29:42,960 --> 00:29:44,960
It just didn't make much sense.

434
00:29:45,200 --> 00:29:46,600
I can see that.

435
00:29:47,120 --> 00:29:49,160
I have no record of this man.

436
00:29:50,840 --> 00:29:54,320
I think, in fact, you have.
If you could take another look.

437
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:57,040
