and abusive.

458
00:31:06,800 --> 00:31:09,520
For God's sake.
I mean, that's just ridiculous.

459
00:31:09,680 --> 00:31:12,800
I was mildly sarcastic,
but under the circumstances...

460
00:31:12,880 --> 00:31:14,800
...I was astonishingly restrained.

