I don't even know the rules.

498
00:33:14,080 --> 00:33:16,800
We'll explain them. It's for a great cause.

499
00:33:23,840 --> 00:33:25,200
Where am I?

500
00:33:25,320 --> 00:33:28,280
I'm your doctor, Mr. Randall.
You're in the hospital.

501
00:33:28,360 --> 00:33:29,440
