00:33:33,240 --> 00:33:35,080
Where are my clothes? My stuff?

504
00:33:35,200 --> 00:33:37,280
They're outside. They're safe.

505
00:33:38,560 --> 00:33:40,200
I was in the park.

506
00:33:40,520 --> 00:33:42,800
It must be pretty confusing, huh?

507
00:33:43,800 --> 00:33:48,360
We were wondering, is there anybody
you'd like us to contact? Any family?

508
00:33:48,640 --> 00:33:50,040
My daughter, but....

509
00:33:50,120 --> 00:33:51,960
When did you see her last?

510
00:33:53,280 --> 00:33:56,000
Not since 1978.

511
00:33:56,520 --> 00:33:57,680
When her mother died.

512
00:33:57,760 --> 00:34:01,880
I see. Anybody else you'd like us
to get in touch with?

513
00:34:02,480 --> 00:34:06,360
No, I'm pretty much on my own now.
Thank you.

514
00:34:08,400 --> 00:34:10,520
Could you stand up for me?

515
00:34:11,080 --> 00:34:13,000
Forgive me for asking...

516
00:34:13,160 --> 00:34:16,040
